}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "Fiwin" and "WU780--021" is silkscreened on the board. :A date code of '''0401''' (First week of 2004) is also on the board.
The MAC/BB included in this device has unknown branding on it ("CGT"?, "CCT"?, "SGT"?, "SCT"?, ???). Per the USB ID, this is a '''SiS''' 162U. :"189162000000", "PPD3164", "0436BZ A1" is on the IC's packaging.
